prodNameC: C 型肝炎一步法快速檢驗試劑
ingredientsDesc:
Each kit contains：
(1) Immunochromatographic testing device：25 pcs or 50 pcs.
1.Device coated Membrane (7mm)：Coat Anti-mouse antibody for reference line 0.001g HCV antigen solution for test line 0.001g.
2.Fiberglass (7mm)：Colloidal gold Au-Ab/Ag conjugate solution for fiberglass coating 0.014g.
(2) Test buffer：1 bottle or 2 bottles.
HCV bovine serum base：bovine serum, 0.85% sodium chloride, Gentamicin sulfate 0.02g/L, 0.05M boric acid, ProClin 300  5ml/L.
Postive control ：buffered protein solution containing human HCV antibody with preservative.
Negative control：buffered protein solution with preservative.
